About Wahoo's
Along the Gordon River, minutes from downtown Naples
Located at the beautiful PORT 32 Naples Marina, Wahoo's River Bar and Grill boasts an island getaway feel. We’re nestled along the Gordon River and just minutes from the old-world charm of downtown Naples. We have a covered outdoor bar, heated pool & spa with live music on weekends. Check out our calendar for our live entertainment. Remember, all Wahoo's River Bar & Grill members and their guests are welcome to use the pool so bring your suit!
Wahoo's River Bar & Grill at PORT 32 Naples Marina is also the perfect place to host your next special occasion, business meeting or family gathering. PORT 32 Naples is also the home of The Flying Bridge and The Clubhouse, serving aged steaks and fresh seafood on the upper level of our clubhouse — another great choice for your upcoming event.
Not a member? No worries! You can dine at Wahoo's River Bar & Grill and receive a complimentary one-day social membership to enjoy our spas. Learn more about our MEMBERSHIP
here
.
The complimentary day pass is free of charge but excludes use of the pool.
We can’t wait for you to enjoy the beautiful waterfront, delicious food & libations, and live tunes while you are at Wahoo’s River Bar and Grill –
see you soon!
